<h1>戾</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#000099;">lì</span><span class=alesi>(li4)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 戾 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 戾</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/perverse" style="color:black;">perverse</a>, <a href="/dictionary/recalcitrant" style="color:black;">recalcitrant</a>, <a href="/dictionary/rebellious" style="color:black;">rebellious</a></p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 8<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 8 strokes: <a href="/character/的" title="de: possessive, adjectival suffix">的</a>, <a href="/character/和" title="he2: harmony, peace; peaceful, calm">和</a>, <a href="/character/国" title="guo2: nation, country, nation-state">国</a>, <a href="/character/到" title="dao4: go to, arrive, been to">到</a>, <a href="/character/所" title="suo3: place, location; numerary adjunct">所</a>, <a href="/character/事" title="shi4: affair, matter, business; to serve; accident, incident">事</a>, <a href="/character/经" title="jing1: classic works; pass through">经</a>, <a href="/character/法" title="fa3: law, rule, regulation, statute; France, French">法</a>, <a href="/character/学" title="xue2: learning, knowledge; school">学</a>, <a href="/character/现" title="xian4: appear, manifest, become visible">现</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/戶" title="Kangxi radical 63">戶</a>&nbsp;63.4</p><p><b>Frequency rank:</b> 4232</p><p><b><a href="/character-list/general-standard" title="Table of General Standard Chinese Characters">General standard</a> index number:</b> 4042</p><p><b>Examples of words containing this character:</b> <a href="/dictionary/乖戾" title="guai1 li4">乖戾</a>, <a href="/dictionary/凶戾" title="xiong1 li4">凶戾</a>, <a href="/dictionary/戾气" title="li4 qi4">戾气</a>, <a href="/dictionary/戾龙" title="li4 long2">戾龙</a>, <a href="/dictionary/暴戾" title="bao4 li4">暴戾</a>, <a href="/dictionary/违戾" title="wei2 li4">违戾</a></p></div><h2>English translation (based on CEDICT):</h2><div class=ceent><div style="background:#dddddd;float:both;font-family: monospace;">戾[<span style="color:#000099;">lì</span>]:</div> <div style="float:left;padding-left:15px;">- to bend<br>- to 